label: inputQuantitySpecifiedEventElement
comment: Information about an event in which a Track and Trace (TT) element of one of more physical or digital objects is identified by a specific object class identifier (such as an electronic product class), either a specific quantity or an unspecified quantity.

domainIncludes.comment: Information about an event that captures the relationship between one or more physical or digital objects identified by identifiers, such as an EPC (Electronic Product Code) or EPC class, that are fully or partially consumed as inputs or as outputs.
